NB. testggev
NB.
NB. Description:
NB.   Test ggevxxx by pair of square matrices
NB.
NB. Syntax:
NB.   testggev AB
NB. where
NB.   AB - 2×n×n-brick
NB.
NB. Formula:
NB.   berr := max(berr0,berr1)
NB. where
