NB.       berr1 := max(| ||r(i)|| - 1 |) / (FP_PREC * n)
NB.   - ggevuvv:
NB.       berr0 := berr(ggevuvn)
NB.       berr1 := berr(ggevunv)
NB.
NB. Notes:
